use ChatGPT to generate a D&D adventure:
1. write a simple module/dungeon
2. put in a random dice generator
3. have chat gpt give a decription of what happens when you roll the dice
4. generate an image that shows the action, maybe even a little animation
5. create a character sheet in the background but the player just prompts with descritions of their actions
6. chat then applies the player action to the character cheet
7. then reinterpret the numbers to narrative